rComments: Ramen Sensei was fantastic. Just go to class, study occasionally, and you're guaranteed an A. I got a 101% on the final, and I loved the class.
Tests are straightforward.  I found it only neccessary to read the short readings and got an A.  She can be helpful if you have a problem.

Was kinda flaky/ditzy and also talked down to the class like we were not intelligent people, which made the lectures a little unpleasant, but she is a very reasonable person.  Subject matter was interesting, though she didn't always know it that well herself.
